top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nirala>Nirala</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>M.C. Hammah</span><br>  Posts: 510<br> <font color=#000000>(7/1/03 1:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=117.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Getting an improvment to Left Axe</span><hr size=1> Personally I'd like to see a 10-15% DW/CD boost and a 15-20% LA boost (based on how they are currently).  I'll back y'all on it though, seems that nerf bat came swingin' in a little hard.  (and having had a full smite cleric I can attest how hard that is!) <p>Nirala Kindred<br>
